{
  "stem": "5551.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In that factory, I-- we again worked as laborers, mainly loading and unloading.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Apparently, this was our trade.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But something that may interest you that happened in Schlieben is Italy had surrendered.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Italy had done away with the fascist regime of-- of Mussolini, as you know, in 1943.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And later on, the Italians run away from the eastern front.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They were stopped by the Germans, and they were now sent to Schlieben as slave laborers.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But they were well fed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That they were strong, young, vigorous.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They had been soldiers.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Once they came to Schlieben, they were under the same regimen that we were.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They received the same food.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They received the same punishment.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They soon organized and blew up the whole outfit.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They blew it all up at night.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "The whole panzerfaust factory went kaput in-- in one night.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And my father was in-- in-- [BACKGROUND NOISE] in the factory at that time of the evening.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I was sure that I will never see my father again, because it was all aflame.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I was in the barracks that evening, but by a miraculous twist, my father survived with very little injury, and we went on to rebuild Schlieben after this blow up.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But this was already the time in history when we witnessed the end coming by the Allied air bombardment.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We could almost set our clocks as the air raids came in.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They came in exactly the same time day and night, and we could see the bombardments of the cities all over, the nearby cities aflame, and we knew then that if we hang in, we may survive-- because at that time, hunger, and hard labor, and exposure were really the only things to kill us.",
      "word_count": 55
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "The murder, the hanging, or killing, or brutality had-- had disappeared.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
